                        <TABLE style="WORD-BREAK: break-all" border=0 width=650><TBODY><TR><TD><div>（1）R<sub>2</sub>；a（2）&nbsp;&nbsp;（3）2.30V（2.29、2.31均正确）&nbsp;&nbsp;（4）94（93、95均正确）<br /><img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/2014082500490949548569.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" /></div></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE><TABLE style="WORD-BREAK: break-all" border=0 width=650><TBODY><TR><TD><div><br />试题分析：（1）根据<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909510625.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，可估算待测电阻约2<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909526333.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，这样<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909542438.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />的总电阻约为5<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909526333.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，滑动变阻器采用限流式接法，阻值约等于待测电阻3—5倍时，测量较准确，因此滑动变阻器选R<sub>2</sub>，另外测量前应将滑动变压器调到最大值，以保护电路，因此触头应调到a端；<br />（2）根据电路图连接实物图，见答案<br />（3）电压表最小刻度是0.1V，读数时应估读到0.01V，因此读数为2.30V；<br />（4）这样测得电阻值为<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/201408250049095731152.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，而<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909604548.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，可得测电阻为<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909620527.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，根据<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909510625.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，代入数据，可得电阻长度<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004909651533.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" /></div></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
